Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:14.18,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Musel jsem ji poslouchat už tisíckrát...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:24.61,YnJ ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\K35}da{\K25}re {\K59}ni {\K39}mo {\K78}{\K28}ki{\K28}zu{\K29}ka{\K28}{\K28}re{\K36}na{\K21}i {\K36}{\K21}i{\K32}ki {\K29}ga {\K31}{\K26}to{\K33}ma{\K23}ru {\K32}yo{\K27}u {\K29}na {\K27}ko{\K37}i {\K29}no {\K23}ko{\K29}ko{\K19}ro
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:24.61,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Mé srdce lapá po dechu, zatímco si nevšímáš mé lásky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:32.99,YnJ ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\K29}bo{\K62}ku{\K57}ra {\K26}wa {\K33}{\K58}na{\K27}ni {\K34}o {\K137}{\K31}o{\K30}i{\K30}ka{\K45}ke{\K72}{\K57}te{\K27}i{\K22}ru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:32.99,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Co je to, za čím se znovu ženeme?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:43.46,YnJ ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\K29}u{\K31}ma{\K26}re{\K26}ta {\K48}ma{\K38}chi {\K48}wa {\K27}{\K42}do{\K42}u{\K33}shi{\K53}te {\K156}{\K41}ko{\K21}n{\K31}na {\K33}ni {\K85}{\K35}ya{\K28}sa{\K26}shi{\K25}i{\K27}n{\K35}da
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:43.46,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Proč se naše rodné město zdá být ke mně tak něžné?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:51.85,YnJ ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\K55}da{\K15}i{\K27}su{\K72}ki {\K32}na {\K23}{\K53}ki{\K31}mi {\K42}ni {\K39}{\K34}ha{\K29}ya{\K34}ku {\K58}a{\K28}i {\K47}ni {\K88}{\K63}yu{\K33}ko{\K23}u
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:51.85,YnJ ED CZ,,0000,0000,0000,,Teď tě zase navštívím, mé milované.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:24:00.85,YnJ ED JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\K29}i{\K29}ma {\K81}ka{\K36}ze {\K37}ni {\K37}{\K35}da{\K60}ka{\K27}re{\K47}te {\K158}{\K16}ha{\K40}shi{\K57}t{\K26}te{\K25}yu{\K52}ku{\K46}n{\K36}da
